      <preamble>
         <formula name="enactingText">
            <p>The Scottish Ministers make the following Regulations in exercise of the powers conferred by section 2(2) of the European Communities Act 1972<noteRef href="#f00001" class="footnote" marker="1"/> and all other powers enabling them to do so.</p>
