         <hcontainer name="regulation" eId="regulation-4">
            <heading>Amendment of the Utilities Contracts (Scotland) Regulations 2016</heading>
            <num>4.</num>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-4-1">
               <num>(1)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>The Utilities Contracts (Scotland) Regulations 2016<noteRef href="#f00009" class="footnote" marker="9"/> are amended in accordance with paragraph (2).</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-4-2">
               <num>(2)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>After regulation 84 (conditions for performance of contracts) insert—<mod>
                        <quotedStructure startQuote="“" endQuote="”" ukl:TargetClass="secondary" ukl:TargetSubClass="unknown" ukl:Context="unknown">
                           <article>
                              <num>84A.</num>
